The,Chinese,Text,Project,API,provides,developers,with,methods,for,integrating,content,and,functionality,of,the,CTP,with,other,web,based,or,web,aware,sites,and,applications,The,API,consists,of,two,main,components,a,plugin,API,which,integrates,external,functionality,into,the,CTP,and,a,JSON,API,which,allows,CTP,functionality,to,be,integrated,into,external,sites,The,Chinese,Text,Project,is,an,open,source,digital,library,that,makes,pre,modern,Chinese,texts,available,globally,to,readers,and,researchers